Package: openlayers
Title: An R Interface to OpenLayers
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Kuethe", email = "crazycapivara@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stefan Kuethe <crazycapivara@gmail.com>
Description: OpenLayers <https://openlayers.org/> is an open-source JavaScript library making it easy
    to put a dynamic map in any web page. This package makes the functionalty of
    the JS library available within R via the htmlwidgets package.
URL: https://github.com/crazycapivara/openlayers/
BugReports: https://github.com/crazycapivara/openlayers/issues/
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
    htmlwidgets,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr,
    readr
Suggests:
    geojsonio,
    sf,
    testthat
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
